Resource Profile: RS Patient

Official URL: https://build.fhir.org/ig/UPM-NTHC/PH-RoadSafetyIG/StructureDefinition/rs-patient Version: 0.3.0
Draft as of 2025-11-05 Computable Name: RSPatient

Patient demographics and identifiers for RS reporting; reuse PH-Core address extensions for barangay/city/province/region.

Usages:

  • Use this Profile: RS Bundle — EMS Submission, RS Bundle — ONEISS Submission and RS Bundle — Post‑Crash Investigation
  • Refer to this Profile: RS AllergyIntolerance, RS Claim, RS Composition — EMS Submission, RS Composition — ONEISS Submission... Show 9 more, RS Composition — Post‑Crash Investigation, RS Condition, RS DocumentReference (Evidence), RS Encounter, RS MedicationStatement, RS Observation, RS Procedure, RS ServiceRequest and RS Task
  • Examples for this Profile: Patient/rs-bundle-example-patient and Patient/rs-example-patient

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
